ht infringement, or that your intellectual property rights have been otherwise violated, please provide our Copyright Agent with a notice containing the following information: </p> <ol type="1" class="customerServiceNormal"> <li> an electronic or physical signature of the person authorized to act on behalf of the owner of the copyright or other intellectual property interest; </li> <li> a description of the copyrighted work or other intellectual property that you claim has been infringed; </li> <li> ', EMPTY_CLOB());
