 your Web browser to enable the Site to "recognize" you every time you visit and to "remember" any information you have saved, such as storage of items in your shopping cart between visits. Fleet Farm does not use cookies to store any of your personal or financial information that you have on your computer. Fleet Farm recognizes that you have a choice to refuse cookies. However, should you decide not to accept cookies from the Site, you will limit the functionality Fleet Farm can provide when you visit the Site. View your browsers help file for more information on cookies. Fleet Farm receives and may store information you enter on the Site or give to our Site in any other way. For example, Fleet Farm collects information you provide when you place an order or register to create an account on the Site. The information may include, without limitation, your first and last name, mailing address, email address, telephone and facsimile numbers, credit card information, and other personal identifying information. If you choose to share any personal information with Fleet Farm, you will see that the amount and type of personal information Fleet Farm requests depends on how you use the Site. It is completely optional for you to engage in these activities. Depending upon the activity, some of the information Fleet Farm asks you to provide is identified as mandatory and some is voluntary. If you do not provide the mandatory information with respect to a particular activity, you will not be able to engage in that activity. ', EMPTY_CLOB());
